      • getBindings

        List<Binding> getBindings(String descriptor)
        Find the list of Binding registered with the given annotation type. This method returns an empty List if no bindings are registered.
        Parameters:
        descriptor - denotes the annotation's type
        Returns:
        the list of Binding registered with the given descriptor, the list may be empty if no bindings are found.
